<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-HK">
  <head>
    <%- include("../partials/head", { title: tournament.name, tournament }) %>
    <style>
      body { font-family: "Noto Sans TC", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; }
      .pv-glow { box-shadow: 0 18px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
      .pv-card { transition: transform .18s ease, box-shadow .18s ease; }
      .pv-card:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.12); }
      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        .pv-card { transition: none; }
        .pv-card:hover { transform: none; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("../partials/nav", { tournament }) %>
    <%- include("../partials/banner", { tournament }) %>

    <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-10">
      <% const open = typeof registrationOpen !== 'undefined' ? !!registrationOpen : true; %>
      <% const deadlineText = (typeof registrationDeadline !== 'undefined' && registrationDeadline) ? new Date(registrationDeadline).toLocaleString("zh-HK", { hour12: false }) : ""; %>
      <% const kidsPerPerson = Math.round(688/2); %>
      <% const adultPerPerson = Math.round(788/2); %>
      <% const wa = typeof whatsappLink !== 'undefined' ? String(whatsappLink || '').trim() : ''; %>
      <% const poster = "/images/tournament-poster.jpg"; %>
      <% const logo = "/images/picklevibes-logo.png"; %>

      <!-- Top section (把吸引人的資料都放到上面) -->
      <section class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-white ring-1 ring-black/5 pv-glow">
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-16 -left-20 h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-pickle-teal/25 blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-20 -right-20 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-pickle-pink/25 blur-3xl"></div>

        <div class="grid gap-6 p-5 md:grid-cols-12 md:gap-8 md:p-8">
          <div class="md:col-span-5">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-black/[0.03] p-3 ring-1 ring-black/10">
              <div class="absolute right-3 top-3 inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-white/85 px-3 py-1 text-sm font-extrabold text-pickle-ink ring-1 ring-black/10">
                <img src="<%= logo %>" alt="" class="h-4 w-4 rounded-full bg-white object-contain ring-1 ring-black/5" />
                兒童書展 暨超級親子用品展特別場
              </div>
              <img
                src="<%= poster %>"
                alt="賽事海報"
                class="aspect-[4/5] w-full rounded-2xl object-cover ring-1 ring-black/10"
                loading="lazy"
              />
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="md:col-span-7">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-sm font-extrabold tracking-widest text-black/60">
              <span class="rounded-full bg-pickle-mist px-3 py-1 ring-1 ring-black/5">亞洲國際博覽館</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-pickle-mist px-3 py-1 ring-1 ring-black/5">兩人一隊</span>
              <span class="rounded-full bg-pickle-mist px-3 py-1 ring-1 ring-black/5">新手友善</span>
            </div>

            <h1 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight text-pickle-ink md:text-5xl">
              大家減齢 x Pickle Vibes 匹克球博覽盃
            </h1>
            <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75 md:text-lg">
              兩人一隊，<span class="font-extrabold text-pickle-ink">小朋友每人 HK$<%= kidsPerPerson %> 起</span>｜<span class="font-extrabold text-pickle-ink">成人/親子每人 HK$<%= adultPerPerson %> 起</span>。打比賽之餘，同場仲有兒童節親子展：一日完成運動、親子同回憶。
            </p>

            <div class="mt-4 grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="pv-card rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-4 ring-1 ring-black/5">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="mt-0.5 inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white text-pickle-ink ring-1 ring-black/10" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="h-5 w-5">
                      <path d="M12 21c5 0 9-3.6 9-8s-4-8-9-8-9 3.6-9 8c0 2 .9 3.9 2.5 5.3L4 21l3.8-1.2c1.2.7 2.7 1.2 4.2 1.2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink">冇 DUPR 都可以參加</div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-black/70">公開/3.0- 及親子組可 NR；小朋友可勾「沒有 DUPR 積分」</div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="pv-card rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-4 ring-1 ring-black/5">
                <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                  <span class="mt-0.5 inline-flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white text-pickle-ink ring-1 ring-black/10" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="h-5 w-5">
                      <path d="M12 7v5l3 2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                      <path d="M21 12a9 9 0 1 1-18 0 9 9 0 0 1 18 0Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  <div>
                    <div class="text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink">截止報名</div>
                    <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-black/70"><%= deadlineText ? deadlineText : '請以報名頁顯示為準' %></div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
              <a
                href="/apply"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-pickle-pink px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-white shadow-sm hover:brightness-95 <%= !open ? 'pointer-events-none opacity-60' : '' %>"
              >
                <span class="mr-2 inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-white/20 ring-1 ring-white/20" aria-hidden="true">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="h-4 w-4 text-white">
                    <path d="M7 7h10v14H7z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    <path d="M9 3v6M15 3v6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/>
                  </svg>
                </span>
                <%= !open ? '報名已截止' : '立即報名' %>
              </a>
              <% if (wa) { %>
                <a
                  href="<%= wa %>"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-pickle-ink ring-1 ring-black/10 hover:bg-black/5"
                >
                  <span class="mr-2 inline-flex h-5 w-5 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-pickle-mist ring-1 ring-black/10" aria-hidden="true">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" class="h-4 w-4 text-pickle-ink">
                      <path d="M12 21c5 0 9-3.6 9-8s-4-8-9-8-9 3.6-9 8c0 2 .9 3.9 2.5 5.3L4 21l3.8-1.2c1.2.7 2.7 1.2 4.2 1.2Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
                    </svg>
                  </span>
                  WhatsApp 查詢 / 配對組別
                </a>
              <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-6 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
              <div class="pv-card rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 ring-1 ring-black/5">
                <div class="text-base font-bold text-black/60">價錢（每人）</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-base font-black text-pickle-ink">HK$<%= kidsPerPerson %> 起</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-black/60">小朋友（HK$688/隊）</div>
              </div>
              <div class="pv-card rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 ring-1 ring-black/5">
                <div class="text-base font-bold text-black/60">成人/親子</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-base font-black text-pickle-ink">HK$<%= adultPerPerson %> 起</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-black/60">HK$788/隊</div>
              </div>
              <div class="pv-card rounded-2xl bg-white p-4 ring-1 ring-black/5">
                <div class="text-base font-bold text-black/60">小朋友年齡</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-base font-extrabold text-pickle-ink">U8/U10/U12/U14</div>
                <div class="mt-1 text-sm text-black/60">各項為「該歲或以下」（含滿歲）</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Info：整段上下留白用 section padding，避免只堆喺字上面 -->
      <section class="mt-8 grid gap-6 py-10 md:grid-cols-2 md:py-14">
        <div class="pv-card rounded-3xl bg-white p-6 ring-1 ring-black/5">
            <div class="mb-2 text-xl font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-2xl">賽事資訊</div>
            <dl class="grid gap-3 text-sm">
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
                <dt class="text-black/60">名稱</dt>
                <dd class="text-right font-semibold text-pickle-ink"><%= tournament.name %></dd>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
                <dt class="text-black/60">日期</dt>
                <dd class="text-right font-semibold text-pickle-ink"><%= tournament.date %></dd>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-4">
                <dt class="text-black/60">地點</dt>
                <dd class="text-right font-semibold text-pickle-ink"><%= tournament.location %></dd>
              </div>
            </dl>

            <div class="mt-5 rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-5 ring-1 ring-black/5">
              <div class="text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">小朋友組年齡</div>
              <div class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-black/75">
                U8＝8歲或以下｜U10＝10歲或以下｜U12＝12歲或以下｜U14＝14歲或以下（按賽事年齡參考日計算，含滿該歲）
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-4 rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-5 ring-1 ring-black/5">
              <div class="text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">點解值得專登去亞博？</div>
              <div class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75">
                唔止係「打一場波」：同場有親子展，你可以當成家庭一日行程（運動＋親子活動＋書展/遊戲）。
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        <div class="pv-card rounded-3xl bg-white p-6 ring-1 ring-black/5">
          <div class="mb-2 text-xl font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-2xl">小朋友組年齡</div>
          <div class="text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75">
            U8＝8歲或以下｜U10＝10歲或以下｜U12＝12歲或以下｜U14＝14歲或以下
          </div>
          <div class="mt-2 text-sm text-black/60">（按賽事年齡參考日計算，含滿該歲）</div>
          <div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-5 ring-1 ring-black/5">
            <div class="text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">新手提示</div>
            <div class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75">
              公開組、DUPR 3.0- 組別及親子組可 NR；小朋友組可勾選「沒有 DUPR 積分」。
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- FAQ (full width) -->
      <section class="mt-8">
        <div class="pv-card rounded-3xl bg-white p-6 ring-1 ring-black/5">
          <div class="text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">常見問題（FAQ）</div>
          <div class="mt-4 space-y-3">
            <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-5 ring-1 ring-black/5" open>
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">
                冇 DUPR 可唔可以參加？
              </summary>
              <div class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75">
                可以。公開組、DUPR 3.0- 組別及親子組可選 NR；小朋友組可勾選「沒有 DUPR 積分」。
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-5 ring-1 ring-black/5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">
                收費係點計？點解要寫「每人價」？
              </summary>
              <div class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75">
                本賽事以兩人一隊報名：小朋友組 HK$688/隊（每人約 HK$<%= kidsPerPerson %>），其他組別 HK$788/隊（每人約 HK$<%= adultPerPerson %>）。
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-5 ring-1 ring-black/5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">
                報名後流程係點？點付款？
              </summary>
              <div class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75">
                填表後會收到電郵紀錄。付款會透過 Stripe 安全付款頁完成（會以電郵提供付款連結及限期）。
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-5 ring-1 ring-black/5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">
                如果付款連結失效點算？
              </summary>
              <div class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75">
                我哋會提供長效付款連結（點入會即時建立 Stripe 付款頁）。如有需要亦可 WhatsApp 聯絡主辦方協助。
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-5 ring-1 ring-black/5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">
                交通去亞博方便嗎？
              </summary>
              <div class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75">
                可乘機鐵到博覽館站，步行可達；如自駕亦可泊車。建議預留交通時間，並可安排同日參觀兒童節親子展。
              </div>
            </details>
            <details class="group rounded-2xl bg-pickle-mist p-5 ring-1 ring-black/5">
              <summary class="cursor-pointer list-none text-lg font-extrabold text-pickle-ink md:text-xl">
                新手／家長會唔會太競技？
              </summary>
              <div class="mt-2 text-base leading-relaxed text-black/75">
                我們設有不同組別（包括 NR/小朋友可不填 DUPR），適合第一次參加比賽的球員及家庭，一齊享受賽事體驗。
              </div>
            </details>
          </div>

          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
            <a
              href="/apply"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-pickle-pink px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-white shadow-sm hover:brightness-95 <%= !open ? 'pointer-events-none opacity-60' : '' %>"
            >
              <%= !open ? '報名已截止' : '立即報名' %>
            </a>
            <% if (wa) { %>
              <a
                href="<%= wa %>"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-2xl bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-extrabold text-pickle-ink ring-1 ring-black/10 hover:bg-black/5"
              >
                WhatsApp 立即查詢
              </a>
            <% } %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>

